        <p data-i18n="about.d1_body">We exist for the in-between moment — when patients are too well for the ICU, but not yet ready for home.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="diff-card">
        <div class="diff-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
